    "      \"D:\\\\anaconda3\\\\Lib\\\\site-packages\\\\sklearn\\\\cluster\\\\_kmeans.py:1436: UserWarning: KMeans is known to have a memory leak on Windows with MKL, when there are less chunks than available threads. You can avoid it by setting the environment variable OMP_NUM_THREADS=1.\\n\",\n",
